ELK
-----
- ElasticSearch -> DB to store log files/Docs
- LogStash -> 
- Kibana -> UI for elastic search 


usually application logs should be shifted for external system
-------------
create an EC2 instance
- t3.large
- sg -allow all 
- 30GB

- configure elastic search
- configure kibana
- configure servers
- configure filebeat(agent)
- to maintain structure logs we need use Logstash
- configure Logstash in ELS master server.
